  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[php获取月初和月尾时间]]></title>
    <link href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2021/01/22/lang-php-month/"/>
    <updated>2021-01-22T21:30:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2021/01/22/lang-php-month</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[#### 获取当前时间的月初月尾
```
	echo date("Y-m-01", time());
	echo PHP_EOL;
	echo date('Y-m-t', time());

	// 输出
	2017-09-01
	2017-09-30
```

#### 获取上一月的月初月尾
```
	echo date("Y-m-01", strtotime('-1 month'));
	echo PHP_EOL;
	echo date('Y-m-t', strtotime('-1 month'));

	// 输出
	2017-08-01
	2017-08-31
```


#### 获取下一月的月初月尾
```
	echo date("Y-m-01", strtotime('+1 month'));
	echo PHP_EOL;
	echo date('Y-m-t', strtotime('+1 month'));

	// 输出
	2017-10-01
	2017-10-31
```

]]></content>
